OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Sir Bernard Ingham, Margaret Thatcher's
OL,6, press chief in Downing Street, has     
OL,7, died, his family have announced.       
OL,9,FKnown for his straight-talking         
OL,10,Fapproach, Sir Bernard served in No 10  
OL,11,Fthroughout Mrs Thatcher's premiership  
OL,12,Ffrom 1979 to 1990.                     
OL,14,FThe former journalist, who was 90, died
OL,15,Fafter a short illness on Friday        
OL,16,Flunchtime surrounded by his family, a  
OL,17,Fstatement said.                        
OL,19,FHis son John said: "My family will miss
OL,20,Fhim greatly.                           
